    • getListeDesLivresCommande

      public List<Livre> getListeDesLivresCommande()
      Returns a list of unique books that are part of this command. Note: This list does not carry the ordered quantity directly; use getQuantiteLivreDansPanier(isbn) or iterate through the map for book-specific quantities in the order.
      Returns:
      A List of Livre objects in the command.
